parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rust and corrosion of the frame can cause structural failure, leading to loss of vehicle control, accidents, and potentially life-threatening incidents.
symptoms: Frame rust
corrosion
and perforation; failure of frame components
such as cross-members and sway bars; creaking and crunching noises when driving or jacking up the vehicle; rust flakes or debris falling from the frame.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the airbag not deploying in the event of a crash, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag does not deploy in a crash
the airbag cover is melted or sticky
a clunking or rattling noise is heard from the airbag compartment.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rust and corrosion of the frame can lead to structural failure, which can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The frame is rusted or corroded
the spare tire carrier is corroded
the spare tire drops from the carrier while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the TAKATA airbag inflator can lead to the airbag not deploying or deploying incorrectly, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag does not deploy in a crash
the airbag inflator is recalled.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rust and corrosion of the frame can cause the vehicle to become unsafe to drive, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The frame is severely rusted
with holes and cracks in the frame
the spare tire is rusted and detached
the steering rack mount is cracked
the ball joints are faulty and rusted
the CV axle boots are destroyed
and the wheel bearings and hub are failing.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The brake failure can cause accidents or injuries, especially when the vehicle is traveling at high speeds.
symptoms: The brake pedal goes to the floor
the brake pedal is soft or spongy
the brakes fail to respond
and the vehicle takes longer to stop.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The suspension failure can cause accidents or injuries, especially when the vehicle is traveling at high speeds.
symptoms: The steering rack mount is cracked
the ball joints are faulty and rusted
the CV axle boots are destroyed
and the wheel bearings and hub are failing.
